---
title: Cauliflower Mac 'n' Cheese with Pancetta, Cavatappi and Scallions
description: Normally, we don’t mess with classics like mac ’n’ cheese. But when our chefs suggested adding some cauliflower and pancetta, there was no doubt that we just had to go there. The result? A dish that’s as genre-bending as it is comforting. It’s proof that vegetables and comfort food can coexist in melty, creamy, tender, and porky harmony.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cauliflower-pancetta-mac-n-cheese-f69048ea.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cauliflower-pancetta-mac-n-cheese-5b5b465e30006c3ad8272442-ad839051.pdf
cuisine: North America
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cauliflower-mac-n-cheese-5b5b465e30006c3ad8272442
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 630 kcal
